    public class NormalRule
extends DefaultRule
    NormalRule extends DefaultRule and represents another type of rules in which the user sets his own metrics and operators.

        NormalRule's Constructor. Creates a new rule with custom metrics and operators
        Parameters:
        ruleName - custom rule name provided by user
        metric1 - custom first metric given by the user (LOC or ATFD, depending on test)
        metric2 - custom first metric given by the user (CYCLO or LAA, depending on test)
        and - custom operator given by the user (or = !and, and = and)
        test - major type of rule that defines this one
